These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, lemon, raspberry, zucchini
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, photography, board-games
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, skateboarding, basketball
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
 4. the person who's sport is handball is not the person eating zucchini##6
 5. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5
 6. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the left of the person eating lemon##8
 8. the person eating lemon is not the person who's sport is basketball##6
 9. the person eating apricot is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person eating lemon is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
12. the person eating lemon is in an even position##4
13. the person eating zucchini is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
14. the person who's hobby is photography is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | apricot         | zucchini     | raspberry     | lemon         |
| Hobby   | gardening | board-games    | photography     | card-games |
| Sport   | handball       | water-polo | basketball | skateboarding       |

