.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, mirinda, 7up, fanta
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, software-developer, accountant
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, lacrosse, tennis, sailing
 1. the software-developer is not to the right of the accountant##8
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is the engineer##1
 5. the dancer is not the person drinking 7up##6
 6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the dancer##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the software-developer##5
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up          | soy-milk      | fanta      | mirinda   |
| Job        | software-developer     | dancer | engineer | accountant      |
| Sport      | sailing | lacrosse    | skiing  | tennis |

