.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, singing, dancing, chess
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, folk, soul, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, boat, quad-bike
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 2. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
 3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 4. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 5. the person driving the motorbike is not the fan of pop##6
 6. the fan of pop is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | dancing  | singing | chess | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | pop      | ambient | soul        |
| Transport     | motorbike | boat       | quad-bike    | bike     |

