.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, drama, time-travel, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, house, gospel, salsa
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, mexican, indian, dutch
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 2. the mexican is not to the left of the fan of house##8
 3. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
 4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the mexican##8
 6. the indian is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
 7. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 9. the argentine is on the left of the indian##1
10. the person watching family movies is the indian##1
11. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | family | drama    | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | house     | rock   | salsa     |
| Nationality   | argentine | indian   | mexican | dutch    |

