 3. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the person watching adventure movies is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
 7. the person who's hobby is camping is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
10. the person who's sport is rugby is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
11. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person watching drama movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
