.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, kale, cauliflower, artichoke
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, time-travel, scientific, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian, italian
 1. the person eating cauliflower is not to the left of the person watching satire movies##8
 2. the person watching spy movies is not the canadian##6
 3. the nigerian is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person watching spy movies##7
 4. the canadian is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person eating artichoke##3
 6. the nigerian is the person watching satire movies##1
 7. the person eating peas is somewhere to the right of the person watching scientific movies##5
 8. the italian is between the person eating peas and the nigerian##2
 9. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person eating peas##8
10. the person eating cauliflower is not to the right of the person eating artichoke##8
11. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | kale      | cauliflower      | artichoke | peas |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | satire    | spy | time-travel     |
| Nationality   | australian    | nigerian | italian  | canadian |

