There 4 different types of food: pear, blueberry, apricot, spinach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, funk, country, electronic
1. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
2. the person eating pear is somewhere between the person eating spinach and the person eating apricot##7
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
4. the fan of country is not to the right of the person drinking 7up##8
5. the person eating spinach is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
6. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
7. the person eating spinach is the fan of funk##1
8. the person eating spinach is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the person drinking hot-chocolate##7
9. the person eating spinach is on the left of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate     | milk | water  | 7up |
| Food          | blueberry | spinach   | pear | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | funk   | electronic      | country      |

