.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-9::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, traveling, puzzles, filmmaking
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, spanish, thai, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, quad-bike, van
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not to the right of the person driving the scooter##8
 2. the turkish is somewhere between the person driving the van and the thai##7
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
 4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
 7. the turkish is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 8. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 9. the person who's hobby is traveling is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
10. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
11. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
13. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | puzzles | filmmaking | traveling    |
| Nationality   | thai  | turkish    | mexican      | spanish |
| Transport     | motorbike | scooter          | van      | quad-bike       |

