 4. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating apple##8
 5. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
10. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##8
