5. the canadian is not the person who's sport is skateboarding##6
6. the turkish is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's sport is soccer##2
7. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rowing##5
8. the canadian is not to the left of the person who's sport is baseball##8
9. the turkish is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |    3     |    4     |
