5. the french is not the person who's sport is tennis##6
6. the owner of the horse is on the left of the turkish##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is rowing##7
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
9. the person who's sport is tennis is the japanese##1

